            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确把《古兰经》整体降示在近天，然后在莱麦丹月的高贵之夜我开始把他降示给穆罕默德（愿主福安之）。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "97:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你怎能知道这夜里的吉庆和福泽呢？</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "97:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这夜是福泽浩荡之夜，对于凭信仰善计算的人，树立起这一夜，胜过一千个月。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "97:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>众天使和吉卜利勒天使，（愿主赐其平安）将奉清高真主之命在这一夜而下降，履行真主在对这年里的给养、死亡、出生等的预定。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "97:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这个吉庆的夜自始至终，直到凌晨都是福泽。</p>"
        }
    }
}